      <h1>Shopify Plus Break-Even Revenue Calculator</h1>
      <p class="intro">Shopify Plus costs £2,300+/month. It pays for itself through lower transaction fees, checkout extensibility, and unlimited staff accounts — but only at a certain revenue level. Find yours.</p>

      <section class="card">
        <p class="card-title">Enter your details</p>
